long_description2: Get fast results for all your steaming and ironing needs and keep your clothes looking perfectly pressed and smelling fresh. Engineered with 1875 watts of power, the Turbo ExtremeSteam Steam & Iron 2-in-1 with Turbo by Conair is a high-heat, handheld garment steamer that doubles as an iron for vertical and horizontal use. The extra-large aluminum soleplate It heats up within seconds. De-wrinkle and freshen clothing, curtains, linens, and more with 4 steam settings.
